Dear Team

Please refer to the attached contract with regards to our discussion.

We have made some adjustments, especially regarding the terms of payment.

We got approval from our management to go ahead with the suggested terms of payment.

Additionally, there is also an issue regarding duration or time of delivery.

Kindly go through and advise on how to proceed.

Hoping for positive feedback and support.


Warm Regards
